                    COMPREHENSIVE PROJECT LICENSE
================================================================================

This license applies to ALL components of the Spiffy Project, including:

1. OMEGA KERNEL (spiffy_ultron_zero_v22/)
   - Python core application
   - C++ network accelerators
   - Rust cryptography accelerators
   - PHP web dashboard
   - Ruby automation DSL
   - Bash deployment scripts
   - Java portable agents

2. SPIFFY OMEGA (spiffy_omega/)
   - C++ implementation
   - Advanced security features

3. SPIFFY CPP (spiffy_cpp/)
   - C++ accelerators and bindings

4. SPIFFY STANDARD SECURITY SUITE (spiffy_standard_security_suite/)
   - Standard security tools

5. ALL DOCUMENTATION
   - README files
   - Deployment guides
   - Usage instructions
   - Technical documentation

6. ALL SUPPORTING FILES
   - Configuration files
   - Build scripts
   - Test files
   - Example workflows

